query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS projectInsights (
    id int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
    projectId int NOT NULL,
    userId int NOT NULL,
    summaryMarkdown mediumtext NOT NULL,
    strengthsJson json,
    weaknessesJson json,
    recommendationsJson json,
    averageScoresJson json,
    trackCount int NOT NULL,
    createdAt timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
    INDEX idx_projectInsights_projectId (projectId),
    CONSTRAINT fk_projectInsights_project FOREIGN KEY (projectId) REFERENCES projects(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    CONSTRAINT fk_projectInsights_user FOREIGN KEY (userId) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
  )
